3 NOW, THEREFORE,
4 Be it resolved by the House of Representatives of the General Assembly of the
5 Commonwealth of Kentucky:
6 Section 1. The members of the House of Representatives hereby recognize
7 August 21, 2025, as Kentucky Senior Citizens Day in the Commonwealth.
8 Section 2. When the House adjourns this day, it does so in honor of all senior
9 citizens and acknowledges their lifetime of invaluable contributions made to both the
10 Commonwealth and this great nation.
11 Section 3. The Clerk of the House is directed to transmit a copy of this
12 Resolution to Representative Beverly Chester-Burton.
